Go/Fiber         →  8080
Node/Express     →  3000
Python/FastAPI   →  8000
React dev        →  3000 (Vite) / 5173 (new Vite)
Nginx            →  80
MySQL            →  3306
PostgreSQL       →  5432
Redis            →  6379
MongoDB          →  27017
